creator: Various
description: LibriVox’s Short Story Collection 058: a collection of 20 short works of fiction in the public domain read by a group of LibriVox members, including stories by Conan Doyle, Wodehouse, Poe, Maupassant, Blackwood, Gogol, Wilkins Freeman and Gibran, read in English by Carina Pereira; Bellona Times; Martin Reyto; Chiquito Crasto; Paul Rizik; Robert Dixon; Lynne Thompson; Phillip Cryan; Phil Schempf; John Deryl; Son of the Exiles. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B 01-10 (136MB) Download M4B 11-20 (148MB)
